Pork Belly:  It wasn't called this but that's what it is --- bacon.
The meat came out frozen so when we grilled it up, it became tough.
I was the most disappointed with this dish.
Overall, I don't think we'd be coming back.
The waitresses were really nice though so don't be frightened away!

